303
00:20:54,840 --> 00:20:56,273
I ain't got the steam no more.

304
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:14,790
A pretty old dog, huh?

305
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:16,675
Had him ever since he was a pup.

306
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,913
He was a good sheep dog when he was young.

307
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:20,870
Over here.

