00:21:37,430 --> 00:21:38,000
Hmm?

313
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,755
What's this?

314
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,001
I don't know.

315
00:21:48,320 --> 00:21:48,991
No?

316
