00:28:25,760 --> 00:28:26,875
And I know he won't let me can ya,

416
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:29,954
But he can't stop me from tanglin with you if you don't lay off my wife.

417
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:33,233
What is it this time, Mr. Jackson?

418
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:34,834
You gave her one of your pups.

419
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:35,645
and?

420
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:37,520
I do not want no ranch hand givin' my wife presents.

421
00:28:37,555 --> 00:28:38,350
and?

422
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,600
She won't give it up, so you've got to take it back.

423
00:28:41,635 --> 00:28:42,749
