432
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:38,874
He was aimin at Lennie.

433
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:41,751
It's like I told you. He hates big guys.

434
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:44,796
Well, come on, you fellas.

435
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:58,549
This here's Slim, fellas.  What Slim says goes around here.

