00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:08,794
My name is George Milton.

441
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:11,237
He's my partner here, Lennie Small.

442
00:30:11,840 --> 00:30:13,045
You fellas travel around together?

443
00:30:13,080 --> 00:30:15,275
Yes, we kind of look out for each other.

