00:30:25,640 --> 00:30:27,039
One white and brown.

449
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,469
Okay, big boy.

450
00:30:28,760 --> 00:30:29,875
We get back to the barn, I'll give you one.

451
00:30:30,440 --> 00:30:31,316
A brown and white one.

