00:32:02,280 --> 00:32:02,917
Yes.

480
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,718
What Candy says about her is right-

481
00:32:38,280 --> 00:32:39,508
Curley has got a pack of trouble.

482
00:32:40,520 --> 00:32:41,475
Gosh, she's pretty.

483
00:32:41,760 --> 00:32:42,670
Now you listen to me-

484
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:44,269
Don't you even look at her!

485
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:46,598
Ah, I never done nothin, George.

486
00:32:47,360 --> 00:32:48,315
No you never.

487
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:51,275
But when she was standin here, you wasn't lookin the other way, neither.

488
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:54,348
I never meant no harm, George- Honest I never.

489
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:56,870
